Leslie S. BOWDEN, Trustee of National Thrift Corporation of America, v. Galen H. WELCH, Collector, etc. No. 7279. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Sept. 6, 1933.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
